{"tid":1509322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有個人同我講左樣我無諗過既野","createTime":"2019-08-26T20:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T05:03:52.000Z","uid":7030,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8c6ac9771bac2a57bcf5afb8275f1bcde99cf257","tid":1509322,"uid":7030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:06:59.000Z","msg":"佢問我<br />\n<br />\n假設我係一個港豬，我份人比較蠢，唔明白香港發生緊咩事，即使你點解釋我都唔明，係一個政治冷感既人。<br />\n<br />\n我純粹係想我依家既生活維持不變，因為我覺得我有飽飯食有工返養活到自己同令到身邊既人生活安好無憂無慮。<br />\n<br />\n但正正因為香港搞成咁，我老細生意下滑，間鋪執左粒，令到我無左份工，我係咁既情況下可以有咩選擇？<br />\n<br />\n姐係假設我係咁既角色，我無任何立場，只係安於本份為左自己同身邊人生活好，咁我今時今日無左份工，我可以有咩選擇？<br />\n<br />\n假如無經濟條件移民，純討論"},{"pid":"aec43e83c3e71f49923ef6d6c6a541532c5968c9","tid":1509322,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=225f45d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=4b5f107f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=bc5ffdba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"0417496e7dfb6581010ae4fd55b5316e8b60a1fc","tid":1509322,"uid":7030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aec43e83c3e71f49923ef6d6c6a541532c5968c9","tid":1509322,"uid":339